Coming in from another room, hearing Waspinator.. rolling her optics.

Going over to Waspinator... grabbing the Predacon roughly... then tossing him 
into a CR rather roughly. "Satisfied?!" she growled, her crimson optics 
glared at Waspinator. 

Looking at the others. "Best we do charge up. I have a feeling we will all 
need it soon enough." she hissed.
